item.title: CVE-2018-16183|2024-08-05T10:17:38.305Z -- panasonic%20corporation -- some%20pre-installed%20applications%20on%20panasonic%20pc
item.description: An unquoted search path vulnerability in some pre-installed applications on Panasonic PC run on Windows 7 (32bit), Windows 7 (64bit), Windows 8 (64bit), Windows 8.1 (64bit), Windows 10 (64bit) delivered in or later than October 2009 allow local users to gain privileges via a Trojan horse executable file and execute arbitrary code with eleveted privileges.
